General.Name: ClimateRock Class A Ordinary Shares
General.Description: ClimateRock focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to pursue an initial business combination within climate change, environment, renewable energy and emerging, and clean technologies. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
